  <prompt>
    Validate Phase C exit gate per spec.md §Phase C Exit Criteria (6 criteria + Q7
    expansion criterion). Walk through each:
    1. Agent has accurate workspace awareness — confirmed by task 078 scenario 1.
    2. "Update the summary in Tab 1" works — confirmed by tasks 055 + 058.
    3. "Send to Workspace" + "Add to Assistant" + "Pin to Matter" all functional —
       confirmed by task 057.
    4. Context pane shows live execution trace in real time — confirmed by tasks 061 +
       062 + 063.
    5. Cross-conversation memory recalls prior-matter context — confirmed by tasks
       064-068 + task 078 scenario 3.
    6. Pinned facts persist as user preferences across sessions — confirmed by tasks
       065 + 069 + task 078 scenario 5.
    7. **Q7**: Pinned Memory CRUD UI in Context pane functional — confirmed by task 070
       + task 078 scenario 6.

    Document each criterion's evidence + sign off. Update plan.md or current-task.md
    with Phase C complete status. Per CLAUDE.md §Confirmation Triggers, Phase C exit
    → D triggers user sign-off before Phase D launches.
  </prompt>

  <role>
    Project lead / senior engineer with familiarity across all Phase C deliverables.
  </role>

  <goal>
    All 6 + Q7 exit criteria validated with evidence; user sign-off captured; Phase D
    cleared to start.
  </goal>

